data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Seller is willing to do an assumable mortgage at a 2.5% rate. Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Deltona, Florida! This beautiful home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering a spacious and comfortable living environment spanning across 1,836 square feet.    Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the harmonious blend of ceramic tile and plush carpet flooring, ensuring both style and comfort underfoot. The open floor concept creates an inviting atmosphere, seamlessly connecting the living and kitchen areas. Natural light floods the interior through large windows, giving the home a bright and airy feel.    The centerpiece of the living space is the expansive kitchen, adorned with sleek stainless steel appliances that perfectly complement the rich cabinetry and granite countertops. The grand kitchen island serves as both a culinary hub and a gathering point for friends and family, making it ideal for entertaining or casual dining.    Retreat to the well-appointed bedrooms, where tranquility and relaxation await. The master suite is a true oasis, complete with an ensuite bathroom featuring modern fixtures. Three additional bedrooms provide ample space for family members or guests, each offering a serene ambiance and plenty of closet space.    Step outside onto the rear patio and immerse yourself in the beauty of the expansive backyard. The patio offers the perfect setting for outdoor dining, relaxation, and creating lasting memories with loved ones. Situated on a generous corner lot, this property boasts remarkable curb appeal and a sense of privacy, enhancing your enjoyment of the outdoor space.    With a 2-car garage, you'll have ample storage space and convenient parking for your vehicles. The meticulous landscaping surrounding the home adds to its overall charm and creates a warm and welcoming first impression.    Located in the vibrant community of Deltona, this home offers easy access to local amenities, schools, parks, and shopping centers. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a space to host gatherings, this home truly has it all. Embrace the Florida lifestyle in this meticulously designed residence that seamlessly combines comfort, style, and functionality. Don't miss your opportunity to make this remarkable property yours!
